{
  "video_id": "U3oI104STzs",
  "title": "Is the \"obesity crisis\" just a disguise for a deeper problem?",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 26146.0,
      "end_time": 27824.0,
      "text": "I'll never forget that day"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 27824.0,
      "end_time": 31723.0,
      "text": "back in the spring of 2006."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 31723.0,
      "end_time": 33302.0,
      "text": "I was a surgical resident"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 33302.0,
      "end_time": 35733.0,
      "text": "at The Johns Hopkins Hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 35733.0,
      "end_time": 37510.0,
      "text": "taking emergency call."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 37510.0,
      "end_time": 40873.0,
      "text": "I got paged by the E.R. around 2 in the morning"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 40873.0,
      "end_time": 42900.0,
      "text": "to come and see a woman with a diabetic ulcer"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 42900.0,
      "end_time": 44694.0,
      "text": "on her foot."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 44694.0,
      "end_time": 48395.0,
      "text": "I can still remember sort of that smell of rotting flesh"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48395.0,
      "end_time": 52022.0,
      "text": "as I pulled the curtain back to see her."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 52022.0,
      "end_time": 54367.0,
      "text": "And everybody there agreed this woman was very sick"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54367.0,
      "end_time": 55719.0,
      "text": "and she needed to be in the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55719.0,
      "end_time": 57319.0,
      "text": "That wasn't being asked."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57319.0,
      "end_time": 59461.0,
      "text": "The question that was being asked of me was a different one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59461.0,
      "end_time": 63390.0,
      "text": "which was, did she also need an amputation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63390.0,
      "end_time": 66357.0,
      "text": "Now, looking back on that night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66357.0,
      "end_time": 71522.0,
      "text": "I'd love so desperately to believe that I treated that woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71522.0,
      "end_time": 74658.0,
      "text": "on that night with the same empathy and compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74658.0,
      "end_time": 78893.0,
      "text": "I'd shown the 27-year-old newlywed"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78893.0,
      "end_time": 80838.0,
      "text": "who came to the E.R. three nights earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80838.0,
      "end_time": 82452.0,
      "text": "with lower back pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82452.0,
      "end_time": 86701.0,
      "text": "that turned out to be advanced pancreatic cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86701.0,
      "end_time": 88864.0,
      "text": "In her case, I knew there was nothing I could do"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88864.0,
      "end_time": 90632.0,
      "text": "that was actually going to save her life."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90632.0,
      "end_time": 92681.0,
      "text": "The cancer was too advanced."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92681.0,
      "end_time": 95361.0,
      "text": "But I was committed to making sure that"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95361.0,
      "end_time": 97784.0,
      "text": "I could do anything possible to make her stay"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 97784.0,
      "end_time": 100207.0,
      "text": "more comfortable. I brought her a warm blanket"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100207.0,
      "end_time": 102927.0,
      "text": "and a cup of a coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102927.0,
      "end_time": 105112.0,
      "text": "I brought some for her parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 105112.0,
      "end_time": 108258.0,
      "text": "But more importantly, see, I passed no judgment on her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 108258.0,
      "end_time": 110155.0,
      "text": "because obviously she had done nothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110155.0,
      "end_time": 112329.0,
      "text": "to bring this on herself."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112329.0,
      "end_time": 115142.0,
      "text": "So why was it that, just a few nights later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115142.0,
      "end_time": 118300.0,
      "text": "as I stood in that same E.R. and determined"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118300.0,
      "end_time": 121711.0,
      "text": "that my diabetic patient did indeed need an amputation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121711.0,
      "end_time": 125615.0,
      "text": "why did I hold her in such bitter contempt?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125615.0,
      "end_time": 128080.0,
      "text": "You see, unlike the woman the night before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128080.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130479.00000000001,
      "text": "this woman had type 2 diabetes."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130479.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132031.0,
      "text": "She was fat."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132031.0,
      "end_time": 133944.0,
      "text": "And we all know that's from eating too much"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 133944.0,
      "end_time": 136299.0,
      "text": "and not exercising enough, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136299.0,
      "end_time": 138983.0,
      "text": "I mean, how hard can it be?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138983.0,
      "end_time": 141344.0,
      "text": "As I looked down at her in the bed, I thought to myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141344.0,
      "end_time": 144232.0,
      "text": "if you just tried caring even a little bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144232.0,
      "end_time": 147222.0,
      "text": "you wouldn't be in this situation at this moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 147222.0,
      "end_time": 148999.0,
      "text": "with some doctor you've never met"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 148999.0,
      "end_time": 152814.0,
      "text": "about to amputate your foot."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152814.0,
      "end_time": 156456.0,
      "text": "Why did I feel justified in judging her?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156456.0,
      "end_time": 159025.0,
      "text": "I'd like to say I don't know."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159025.0,
      "end_time": 161061.0,
      "text": "But I actually do."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161061.0,
      "end_time": 163392.0,
      "text": "You see, in the hubris of my youth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163392.0,
      "end_time": 166496.0,
      "text": "I thought I had her all figured out."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 166496.0,
      "end_time": 168326.0,
      "text": "She ate too much. She got unlucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 168326.0,
      "end_time": 171695.0,
      "text": "She got diabetes. Case closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 171695.0,
      "end_time": 173098.0,
      "text": "Ironically, at that time in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 173098.0,
      "end_time": 175496.0,
      "text": "I was also doing cancer research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 175496.0,
      "end_time": 177839.0,
      "text": "immune-based therapies for melanoma, to be specific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 177839.0,
      "end_time": 181812.0,
      "text": "and in that world I was actually taught to question everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181812.0,
      "end_time": 183848.0,
      "text": "to challenge all assumptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183848.0,
      "end_time": 187658.0,
      "text": "and hold them to the highest possible scientific standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187658.0,
      "end_time": 191034.0,
      "text": "Yet when it came to a disease like diabetes"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191034.0,
      "end_time": 194583.0,
      "text": "that kills Americans eight times more frequently than melanoma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 194583.0,
      "end_time": 198011.0,
      "text": "I never once questioned the conventional wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 198011.0,
      "end_time": 201057.0,
      "text": "I actually just assumed the pathologic sequence of events"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 201057.0,
      "end_time": 203642.0,
      "text": "was settled science."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 203642.0,
      "end_time": 207042.0,
      "text": "Three years later, I found out how wrong I was."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207042.0,
      "end_time": 209642.0,
      "text": "But this time, I was the patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 209642.0,
      "end_time": 213473.0,
      "text": "Despite exercising three or four hours every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 213473.0,
      "end_time": 216038.0,
      "text": "and following the food pyramid to the letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216038.0,
      "end_time": 218195.0,
      "text": "I'd gained a lot of weight and developed something"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 218195.0,
      "end_time": 220480.0,
      "text": "called metabolic syndrome."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 220480.0,
      "end_time": 222464.0,
      "text": "Some of you may have heard of this."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 222464.0,
      "end_time": 225909.0,
      "text": "I had become insulin-resistant."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 225909.0,
      "end_time": 228358.0,
      "text": "You can think of insulin as this master hormone"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228358.0,
      "end_time": 232421.0,
      "text": "that controls what our body does with the foods we eat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 232421.0,
      "end_time": 234535.0,
      "text": "whether we burn it or store it."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 234535.0,
      "end_time": 237349.0,
      "text": "This is called fuel partitioning in the lingo."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 237349.0,
      "end_time": 240525.0,
      "text": "Now failure to produce enough insulin is incompatible with life."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 240525.0,
      "end_time": 243181.0,
      "text": "And insulin resistance, as its name suggests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 243181.0,
      "end_time": 245861.0,
      "text": "is when your cells get increasingly resistant"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 245861.0,
      "end_time": 249374.0,
      "text": "to the effect of insulin trying to do its job."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 249374.0,
      "end_time": 251550.0,
      "text": "Once you're insulin-resistant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 251550.0,
      "end_time": 252925.0,
      "text": "you're on your way to getting diabetes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 252925.0,
      "end_time": 254989.0,
      "text": "which is what happens when your pancreas"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 254989.0,
      "end_time": 258312.0,
      "text": "can't keep up with the resistance and make enough insulin."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 258312.0,
      "end_time": 260940.0,
      "text": "Now your blood sugar levels start to rise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 260940.0,
      "end_time": 263572.0,
      "text": "and an entire cascade of pathologic events"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 263572.0,
      "end_time": 267273.0,
      "text": "sort of spirals out of control that can lead to heart disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 267273.0,
      "end_time": 270882.0,
      "text": "cancer, even Alzheimer's disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 270882.0,
      "end_time": 275764.0,
      "text": "and amputations, just like that woman a few years earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275764.0,
      "end_time": 278725.0,
      "text": "With that scare, I got busy changing my diet radically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 278725.0,
      "end_time": 280902.0,
      "text": "adding and subtracting things most of you would find"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 280902.0,
      "end_time": 283982.0,
      "text": "almost assuredly shocking."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 283982.0,
      "end_time": 287861.0,
      "text": "I did this and lost 40 pounds, weirdly while exercising less."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 287861.0,
      "end_time": 290902.0,
      "text": "I, as you can see, I guess I'm not overweight anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 290902.0,
      "end_time": 293069.0,
      "text": "More importantly, I don't have insulin resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 293069.0,
      "end_time": 295113.0,
      "text": "But most important, I was left"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 295113.0,
      "end_time": 298962.0,
      "text": "with these three burning questions that wouldn't go away:"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 298962.0,
      "end_time": 301411.0,
      "text": "How did this happen to me if I was supposedly"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 301411.0,
      "end_time": 304108.0,
      "text": "doing everything right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 304108.0,
      "end_time": 307143.0,
      "text": "If the conventional wisdom about nutrition had failed me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 307143.0,
      "end_time": 310930.0,
      "text": "was it possible it was failing someone else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 310930.0,
      "end_time": 312830.0,
      "text": "And underlying these questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 312830.0,
      "end_time": 316076.0,
      "text": "I became almost maniacally obsessed"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 316076.0,
      "end_time": 318803.0,
      "text": "in trying to understand the real relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 318803.0,
      "end_time": 322433.0,
      "text": "between obesity and insulin resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 322433.0,
      "end_time": 325249.0,
      "text": "Now, most researchers believe obesity"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 325249.0,
      "end_time": 328641.0,
      "text": "is the cause of insulin resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 328641.0,
      "end_time": 330756.0,
      "text": "Logically, then, if you want to treat insulin resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 330756.0,
      "end_time": 332648.0,
      "text": "you get people to lose weight, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 332648.0,
      "end_time": 335412.0,
      "text": "You treat the obesity."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 335412.0,
      "end_time": 338118.0,
      "text": "But what if we have it backwards?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 338118.0,
      "end_time": 341489.0,
      "text": "What if obesity isn't the cause of insulin resistance at all?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 341489.0,
      "end_time": 345409.0,
      "text": "In fact, what if it's a symptom of a much deeper problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 345409.0,
      "end_time": 348231.0,
      "text": "the tip of a proverbial iceberg?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 348231.0,
      "end_time": 350874.0,
      "text": "I know it sounds crazy because we're obviously in the midst"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 350874.0,
      "end_time": 354093.0,
      "text": "of an obesity epidemic, but hear me out."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 354093.0,
      "end_time": 357307.0,
      "text": "What if obesity is a coping mechanism"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 357307.0,
      "end_time": 360909.0,
      "text": "for a far more sinister problem going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 360909.0,
      "end_time": 362391.0,
      "text": "underneath the cell?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 362391.0,
      "end_time": 364757.0,
      "text": "I'm not suggesting that obesity is benign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 364757.0,
      "end_time": 367060.0,
      "text": "but what I am suggesting is it may be the lesser"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 367060.0,
      "end_time": 369771.0,
      "text": "of two metabolic evils."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 369771.0,
      "end_time": 372790.0,
      "text": "You can think of insulin resistance as the reduced capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 372790.0,
      "end_time": 374777.0,
      "text": "of ourselves to partition fuel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 374777.0,
      "end_time": 377068.0,
      "text": "as I alluded to a moment ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 377068.0,
      "end_time": 378990.0,
      "text": "taking those calories that we take in"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 378990.0,
      "end_time": 382429.0,
      "text": "and burning some appropriately and storing some appropriately."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 382429.0,
      "end_time": 384071.0,
      "text": "When we become insulin-resistant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 384071.0,
      "end_time": 387438.0,
      "text": "the homeostasis in that balance deviates from this state."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 387438.0,
      "end_time": 389566.0,
      "text": "So now, when insulin says to a cell,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 389566.0,
      "end_time": 391611.0,
      "text": "I want you to burn more energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 391611.0,
      "end_time": 394046.0,
      "text": "than the cell considers safe, the cell, in effect, says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 394046.0,
      "end_time": 398478.0,
      "text": "\"No thanks, I'd actually rather store this energy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 398478.0,
      "end_time": 400380.0,
      "text": "And because fat cells are actually missing most of"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 400380.0,
      "end_time": 403182.0,
      "text": "the complex cellular machinery found in other cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 403182.0,
      "end_time": 405953.0,
      "text": "it's probably the safest place to store it."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 405953.0,
      "end_time": 410922.0,
      "text": "So for many of us, about 75 million Americans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 410922.0,
      "end_time": 414537.0,
      "text": "the appropriate response to insulin resistance"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 414537.0,
      "end_time": 419466.0,
      "text": "may actually be to store it as fat, not the reverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 419466.0,
      "end_time": 424810.0,
      "text": "getting insulin resistance in response to getting fat."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 424810.0,
      "end_time": 426985.0,
      "text": "This is a really subtle distinction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 426985.0,
      "end_time": 430352.0,
      "text": "but the implication could be profound."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 430352.0,
      "end_time": 432850.0,
      "text": "Consider the following analogy:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 432850.0,
      "end_time": 435819.0,
      "text": "Think of the bruise you get on your shin"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 435819.0,
      "end_time": 439411.0,
      "text": "when you inadvertently bang your leg into the coffee table."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 439411.0,
      "end_time": 442298.0,
      "text": "Sure, the bruise hurts like hell, and you almost certainly"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 442298.0,
      "end_time": 445279.0,
      "text": "don't like the discolored look, but we all know"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 445279.0,
      "end_time": 448732.0,
      "text": "the bruise per se is not the problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 448732.0,
      "end_time": 452474.0,
      "text": "In fact, it's the opposite. It's a healthy response to the trauma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 452474.0,
      "end_time": 455235.0,
      "text": "all of those immune cells rushing to the site of the injury"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 455235.0,
      "end_time": 458219.0,
      "text": "to salvage cellular debris and prevent the spread"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 458219.0,
      "end_time": 460917.0,
      "text": "of infection to elsewhere in the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 460917.0,
      "end_time": 464639.0,
      "text": "Now, imagine we thought bruises were the problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 464639.0,
      "end_time": 467507.0,
      "text": "and we evolved a giant medical establishment"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 467507.0,
      "end_time": 470647.0,
      "text": "and a culture around treating bruises:"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 470647.0,
      "end_time": 473930.0,
      "text": "masking creams, painkillers, you name it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 473930.0,
      "end_time": 476156.0,
      "text": "all the while ignoring the fact that people"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 476156.0,
      "end_time": 479776.0,
      "text": "are still banging their shins into coffee tables."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 479776.0,
      "end_time": 482979.0,
      "text": "How much better would we be if we treated the cause --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 482979.0,
      "end_time": 484544.0,
      "text": "telling people to pay attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 484544.0,
      "end_time": 486147.0,
      "text": "when they walk through the living room --"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 486147.0,
      "end_time": 489420.0,
      "text": "rather than the effect?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 489420.0,
      "end_time": 491297.0,
      "text": "Getting the cause and the effect right"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 491297.0,
      "end_time": 493776.0,
      "text": "makes all the difference in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 493776.0,
      "end_time": 496855.0,
      "text": "Getting it wrong, and the pharmaceutical industry"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 496855.0,
      "end_time": 499535.0,
      "text": "can still do very well for its shareholders"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 499535.0,
      "end_time": 503451.0,
      "text": "but nothing improves for the people with bruised shins."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 503451.0,
      "end_time": 506295.0,
      "text": "Cause and effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 506295.0,
      "end_time": 508132.0,
      "text": "So what I'm suggesting is"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 508132.0,
      "end_time": 510889.0,
      "text": "maybe we have the cause and effect wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 510889.0,
      "end_time": 513523.0,
      "text": "on obesity and insulin resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 513523.0,
      "end_time": 515300.0,
      "text": "Maybe we should be asking ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 515299.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519184.99999999994,
      "text": "is it possible that insulin resistance causes weight gain"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 519184.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521250.99999999994,
      "text": "and the diseases associated with obesity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 521251.0,
      "end_time": 522781.0,
      "text": "at least in most people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 522780.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525781.0,
      "text": "What if being obese is just a metabolic response"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 525781.0,
      "end_time": 528002.0,
      "text": "to something much more threatening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 528002.0,
      "end_time": 530213.0,
      "text": "an underlying epidemic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 530213.0,
      "end_time": 532770.0,
      "text": "the one we ought to be worried about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 532770.0,
      "end_time": 534242.0,
      "text": "Let's look at some suggestive facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 534242.0,
      "end_time": 536728.0,
      "text": "We know that 30 million obese Americans"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 536728.0,
      "end_time": 539701.0,
      "text": "in the United States don't have insulin resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 539701.0,
      "end_time": 541638.0,
      "text": "And by the way, they don't appear to be at any"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 541638.0,
      "end_time": 544718.0,
      "text": "greater risk of disease than lean people."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 544718.0,
      "end_time": 547602.0,
      "text": "Conversely, we know that six million lean people"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 547602.0,
      "end_time": 551039.0,
      "text": "in the United States are insulin-resistant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 551039.0,
      "end_time": 554106.0,
      "text": "and by the way, they appear to be at even greater risk"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 554106.0,
      "end_time": 556261.0,
      "text": "for those metabolic disease I mentioned a moment ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 556261.0,
      "end_time": 558083.0,
      "text": "than their obese counterparts."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 558083.0,
      "end_time": 560320.0,
      "text": "Now I don't know why, but it might be because,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 560320.0,
      "end_time": 563010.0,
      "text": "in their case, their cells haven't actually figured out"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 563010.0,
      "end_time": 566295.0,
      "text": "the right thing to do with that excess energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 566295.0,
      "end_time": 569614.0,
      "text": "So if you can be obese and not have insulin resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 569614.0,
      "end_time": 571485.0,
      "text": "and you can be lean and have it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 571485.0,
      "end_time": 575918.0,
      "text": "this suggests that obesity may just be a proxy"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 575918.0,
      "end_time": 578942.0,
      "text": "for what's going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 578942.0,
      "end_time": 581357.0,
      "text": "So what if we're fighting the wrong war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 581357.0,
      "end_time": 585157.0,
      "text": "fighting obesity rather than insulin resistance?"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 585157.0,
      "end_time": 588400.0,
      "text": "Even worse, what if blaming the obese"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 588400.0,
      "end_time": 591125.0,
      "text": "means we're blaming the victims?"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 591125.0,
      "end_time": 594844.0,
      "text": "What if some of our fundamental ideas about obesity"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 594844.0,
      "end_time": 596702.0,
      "text": "are just wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 596702.0,
      "end_time": 600825.0,
      "text": "Personally, I can't afford the luxury of arrogance anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 600825.0,
      "end_time": 603408.0,
      "text": "let alone the luxury of certainty."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 603408.0,
      "end_time": 606254.0,
      "text": "I have my own ideas about what could be at the heart of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 606254.0,
      "end_time": 608166.0,
      "text": "but I'm wide open to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 608166.0,
      "end_time": 610885.0,
      "text": "Now, my hypothesis, because everybody always asks me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 610885.0,
      "end_time": 612502.0,
      "text": "is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 612502.0,
      "end_time": 615631.0,
      "text": "If you ask yourself, what's a cell trying to protect itself from"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 615631.0,
      "end_time": 617358.0,
      "text": "when it becomes insulin resistant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 617358.0,
      "end_time": 620033.0,
      "text": "the answer probably isn't too much food."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 620033.0,
      "end_time": 623683.0,
      "text": "It's more likely too much glucose: blood sugar."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 623683.0,
      "end_time": 625977.0,
      "text": "Now, we know that refined grains and starches"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 625977.0,
      "end_time": 628033.0,
      "text": "elevate your blood sugar in the short run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 628033.0,
      "end_time": 629941.0,
      "text": "and there's even reason to believe that sugar"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 629941.0,
      "end_time": 632742.0,
      "text": "may lead to insulin resistance directly."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 632742.0,
      "end_time": 636837.0,
      "text": "So if you put these physiological processes to work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 636837.0,
      "end_time": 640310.0,
      "text": "I'd hypothesize that it might be our increased intake"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 640310.0,
      "end_time": 643173.0,
      "text": "of refined grains, sugars and starches that's driving"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 643173.0,
      "end_time": 647824.0,
      "text": "this epidemic of obesity and diabetes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 647824.0,
      "end_time": 649662.0,
      "text": "but through insulin resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 649662.0,
      "end_time": 653574.0,
      "text": "you see, and not necessarily through just overeating and under-exercising."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 653574.0,
      "end_time": 656159.0,
      "text": "When I lost my 40 pounds a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 656159.0,
      "end_time": 658759.0,
      "text": "I did it simply by restricting those things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 658759.0,
      "end_time": 662215.0,
      "text": "which admittedly suggests I have a bias"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 662215.0,
      "end_time": 664576.0,
      "text": "based on my personal experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 664576.0,
      "end_time": 667231.0,
      "text": "But that doesn't mean my bias is wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 667231.0,
      "end_time": 671184.0,
      "text": "and most important, all of this can be tested scientifically."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 671184.0,
      "end_time": 674291.0,
      "text": "But step one is accepting the possibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 674291.0,
      "end_time": 676663.0,
      "text": "that our current beliefs about obesity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 676663.0,
      "end_time": 679669.0,
      "text": "diabetes and insulin resistance could be wrong"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 679669.0,
      "end_time": 682544.0,
      "text": "and therefore must be tested."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 682544.0,
      "end_time": 684935.0,
      "text": "I'm betting my career on this."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 684935.0,
      "end_time": 689060.0,
      "text": "Today, I devote all of my time to working on this problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 689060.0,
      "end_time": 692233.0,
      "text": "and I'll go wherever the science takes me."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 692233.0,
      "end_time": 695764.0,
      "text": "I've decided that what I can't and won't do anymore"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 695764.0,
      "end_time": 698808.0,
      "text": "is pretend I have the answers when I don't."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 698808.0,
      "end_time": 702916.0,
      "text": "I've been humbled enough by all I don't know."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 702916.0,
      "end_time": 705073.0,
      "text": "For the past year, I've been fortunate enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 705073.0,
      "end_time": 708486.0,
      "text": "to work on this problem with the most amazing team"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 708486.0,
      "end_time": 711890.0,
      "text": "of diabetes and obesity researchers in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 711890.0,
      "end_time": 713195.0,
      "text": "and the best part is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 713195.0,
      "end_time": 717094.0,
      "text": "just like Abraham Lincoln surrounded himself with a team of rivals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 717094.0,
      "end_time": 718590.0,
      "text": "we've done the same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 718590.0,
      "end_time": 721853.0,
      "text": "We've recruited a team of scientific rivals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 721853.0,
      "end_time": 725298.0,
      "text": "the best and brightest who all have different hypotheses"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 725298.0,
      "end_time": 726912.0,
      "text": "for what's at the heart of this epidemic."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 726912.0,
      "end_time": 729293.0,
      "text": "Some think it's too many calories consumed."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 729293.0,
      "end_time": 731672.0,
      "text": "Others think it's too much dietary fat."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 731672.0,
      "end_time": 735142.0,
      "text": "Others think it's too many refined grains and starches."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 735142.0,
      "end_time": 737750.0,
      "text": "But this team of multi-disciplinary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 737750.0,
      "end_time": 740734.0,
      "text": "highly skeptical and exceedingly talented researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 740734.0,
      "end_time": 743022.0,
      "text": "do agree on two things."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 743022.0,
      "end_time": 746671.0,
      "text": "First, this problem is just simply too important"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 746671.0,
      "end_time": 749414.0,
      "text": "to continue ignoring because we think we know the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 749414.0,
      "end_time": 752198.0,
      "text": "And two, if we're willing to be wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 752198.0,
      "end_time": 754735.0,
      "text": "if we're willing to challenge the conventional wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 754735.0,
      "end_time": 757798.0,
      "text": "with the best experiments science can offer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 757798.0,
      "end_time": 760103.0,
      "text": "we can solve this problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 760103.0,
      "end_time": 763158.0,
      "text": "I know it's tempting to want an answer right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 763158.0,
      "end_time": 767655.0,
      "text": "some form of action or policy, some dietary prescription --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 767655.0,
      "end_time": 769384.0,
      "text": "eat this, not that —"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 769384.0,
      "end_time": 771064.0,
      "text": "but if we want to get it right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 771064.0,
      "end_time": 773298.0,
      "text": "we're going to have to do much more rigorous science"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 773298.0,
      "end_time": 776151.0,
      "text": "before we can write that prescription."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 776151.0,
      "end_time": 778750.0,
      "text": "Briefly, to address this, our research program"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 778750.0,
      "end_time": 781993.0,
      "text": "is focused around three meta-themes, or questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 781993.0,
      "end_time": 784888.0,
      "text": "First, how do the various foods we consume"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 784888.0,
      "end_time": 787689.0,
      "text": "impact our metabolism, hormones and enzymes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 787689.0,
      "end_time": 790507.0,
      "text": "and through what nuanced molecular mechanisms?"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 790507.0,
      "end_time": 792757.0,
      "text": "Second, based on these insights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 792757.0,
      "end_time": 795716.0,
      "text": "can people make the necessary changes in their diets"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 795716.0,
      "end_time": 799447.0,
      "text": "in a way that's safe and practical to implement?"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 799447.0,
      "end_time": 802456.0,
      "text": "And finally, once we identify what safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 802456.0,
      "end_time": 805484.0,
      "text": "and practical changes people can make to their diet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 805484.0,
      "end_time": 809159.0,
      "text": "how can we move their behavior in that direction"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 809159.0,
      "end_time": 811412.0,
      "text": "so that it becomes more the default"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 811412.0,
      "end_time": 813268.0,
      "text": "rather than the exception?"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 819268.0,
      "end_time": 821688.0,
      "text": "Just because you know what to do doesn't mean"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 821688.0,
      "end_time": 823197.0,
      "text": "you're always going to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 823197.0,
      "end_time": 825325.0,
      "text": "Sometimes we have to put cues around people"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 825325.0,
      "end_time": 827628.0,
      "text": "to make it easier, and believe it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 827628.0,
      "end_time": 831269.0,
      "text": "that can be studied scientifically."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 831269.0,
      "end_time": 833853.0,
      "text": "I don't know how this journey is going to end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 833853.0,
      "end_time": 838066.0,
      "text": "but this much seems clear to me, at least:"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 838066.0,
      "end_time": 843062.0,
      "text": "We can't keep blaming our overweight and diabetic patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 843062.0,
      "end_time": 845974.0,
      "text": "like I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 845974.0,
      "end_time": 848253.0,
      "text": "Most of them actually want to do the right thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 848253.0,
      "end_time": 851622.0,
      "text": "but they have to know what that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 851622.0,
      "end_time": 854668.0,
      "text": "and it's got to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 854668.0,
      "end_time": 859364.0,
      "text": "I dream of a day when our patients can"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 859364.0,
      "end_time": 861099.0,
      "text": "shed their excess pounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 861099.0,
      "end_time": 863912.0,
      "text": "and cure themselves of insulin resistance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 863912.0,
      "end_time": 866642.0,
      "text": "because as medical professionals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 866642.0,
      "end_time": 868612.0,
      "text": "we've shed our excess mental baggage"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 868612.0,
      "end_time": 871938.0,
      "text": "and cured ourselves of new idea resistance sufficiently"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 871938.0,
      "end_time": 875028.0,
      "text": "to go back to our original ideals:"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 875028.0,
      "end_time": 879445.0,
      "text": "open minds, the courage to throw out yesterday's ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 879445.0,
      "end_time": 882773.0,
      "text": "when they don't appear to be working,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 882773.0,
      "end_time": 885892.0,
      "text": "and the understanding that scientific truth isn't final,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 885892.0,
      "end_time": 888640.0,
      "text": "but constantly evolving."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 888640.0,
      "end_time": 891932.0,
      "text": "Staying true to that path will be better for our patients"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 891932.0,
      "end_time": 895180.0,
      "text": "and better for science."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 895180.0,
      "end_time": 898174.0,
      "text": "If obesity is nothing more than a proxy"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 898174.0,
      "end_time": 900100.0,
      "text": "for metabolic illness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 900100.0,
      "end_time": 905397.0,
      "text": "what good does it do us to punish those with the proxy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 905397.0,
      "end_time": 909941.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I think back to that night in the E.R."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 909941.0,
      "end_time": 912254.0,
      "text": "seven years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 912254.0,
      "end_time": 915878.0,
      "text": "I wish I could speak with that woman again."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 915878.0,
      "end_time": 919133.0,
      "text": "I'd like to tell her how sorry I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 919133.0,
      "end_time": 922020.0,
      "text": "I'd say, as a doctor, I delivered"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 922020.0,
      "end_time": 925680.0,
      "text": "the best clinical care I could,"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 925680.0,
      "end_time": 929577.0,
      "text": "but as a human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 929577.0,
      "end_time": 931985.0,
      "text": "I let you down."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 931985.0,
      "end_time": 936230.0,
      "text": "You didn't need my judgment and my contempt."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 936230.0,
      "end_time": 940728.0,
      "text": "You needed my empathy and compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 940728.0,
      "end_time": 943723.0,
      "text": "and above all else, you needed a doctor"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 943723.0,
      "end_time": 945352.0,
      "text": "who was willing to consider"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 945352.0,
      "end_time": 948416.0,
      "text": "maybe you didn't let the system down."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 948416.0,
      "end_time": 951634.0,
      "text": "Maybe the system, of which I was a part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 951634.0,
      "end_time": 954073.0,
      "text": "was letting you down."
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 954073.0,
      "end_time": 956874.0,
      "text": "If you're watching this now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 956874.0,
      "end_time": 961112.0,
      "text": "I hope you can forgive me."
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 961112.0,
      "end_time": 965112.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}